metadata.name: CRYPTO DOLT
metadata.description:
Crypto Dolt (MR.DOLT#13/13) was first sold at "To The Moon" Auction by Bangkok Art Auction Center on 19 March 2022 for 200,000 Thai Baht (approximately 6,000 USD)

This piece contains a character inspired by the artist's work from his time as a college student. In it, Line Censor depicts the character as a creature created in the future with technology, dreams, and imagination, fortelling the exciting intertwined world of Cryptocurrency and reality through symbolic human expressions.
